   Vulnerability Information
   __________________________________________________

   The following vulnerability information is provided to IT product
   developers, integrators, certifiers, accreditors and consumers to
   support the processes of IT security requirements definition,
   specification, testing, evaluation, and assessment.
     * NIST Vulnerability Metabase (ICAT)

     * Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures (CVE)

